-- Gazprom, Oil India to Discuss  Natural Gas Joint Venture Projects in India
-- B y   A n n a   S h i r y a e v s k a y a
-- 2010-12-13T08:47:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-13/gazprom-oil-india-discuss-joint-natural-gas-projects-in-india.html
OAO Gazprom will meet with Oil India
Ltd. in Moscow tomorrow to consider two possible joint natural-
gas projects in India, Alexander Nikiforov, Gazprom’s head for
the country, told reporters in Moscow today.  Oil India and Gazprom may jointly operate the projects that
include onland and offshore blocks, he said. Gazprom hasn’t yet
decided to bid in India’s ninth licensing round, he said  Gazprom will open a permanent office in New Dehli for work
in India, Sri Lanka and Bangladesh, Nikiforov said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anna Shiryaevskaya in Moscow at 
 ashiryaevska@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
